Consultant - PT PricewaterhouseCoopers Indonesia Advisory (PwC Indonesia)
Consultant  -
Consultant
Responsibilities
As consultant, you are part of team who engage for helping client organisations to work smarter and grow faster. You also responsible to consult with clients to build effective organisations, innovate & grow, reduce costs, manage risk & regulation and leverage talent. The aim is to support in designing, managing and executing lasting beneficial change. Build your unique career with PwC Consulting, and become a member of PwC’s South East Asia Consulting. Our diverse professionals bring a wealth of experience from business, government and academia—helping our clients from strategy through execution to close the gap between ideas and results.It is all about you. Your personal and professional development, your achievement, your life long learning, your individuality, and your choices. Requirements:1. Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree, Master's Degree / Post Graduate Degree from Engineering (Environmental/Health/Safety), Engineering (Industrial), Computer Science/Information Technology, Business Studies/Administration/Management, Economics, Finance/Accountancy/Banking or equivalent .   2. GPA minimum 3.00 out of 4.003. Excellent communication in English, both oral and written4. Strong analytical skill, creative thinking, project management skills5. Teamwork capabilities with strong client orientation drive6. Will be graduated in June 2014 or earlier                                                                                                                                                                                                 How to apply :We exclusively invite you to submit your application letter, resume and current official academic transcript to : recruitment.graduate@id.pwc.com at the latest 15 May 2014.Please stated on your subject of email : [Graduate] [Position] [Your Name] [Name of University] [GPA]For example : [Graduate] [Consultant] [Kemal Pasha] [UI] [3.5] For further details, check our website: www.pwc.com/id/careers
